{"tid":2439842,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"唉 有兩份level 1卷比人放咗上連登 好驚比女朋友發現我啲字跡","createTime":"2021-03-09T13:51:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-09T17:09:59.000Z","uid":159653,"like":6,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1729fdb15c256f746e1a6e24d0473c43e9ed76c3","tid":2439842,"uid":159653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T13:51:17.000Z","msg":"想問下有無人試過天生右手中途轉咗左手寫字<br />\n好驚比女朋友知道我攞過level 1<br />\n因為我同女朋友係喺HKU Library識嘅<br />\n但其實識佢嗰日只係跟老豆返工（整電燈）<br />\n未開工坐低休息嗰陣因為見到有位女同學跌親<br />\n我扶起咗佢兼食lunch又相遇 <br />\n於是我地交換咗電話 熟落咗就一齊 <br />\n但係我驚我襯佢唔起<br />\n就呃咗佢話我讀art（因為我唔識字只可以扮藝術家）<br />\n<br />\n依家鋪天蓋地都見到我手柒字 但我同我女朋友都係相愛嘅 唔想因為木門對竹門而分手"},{"pid":"9ff22294793d75c9dafbeeb7b333d89526548727","tid":2439842,"uid":199804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T13:52:09.000Z","msg":"食左先講 食左先講"},{"pid":"735e2c3d4c654b7f0a040900863966b1a866992e","tid":2439842,"uid":159653,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9ff22294793d75c9dafbeeb7b333d89526548727","tid":2439842,"uid":199804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T13:52:09.000Z","msg":"食左先講 食左先講"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T13:56:29.000Z","msg":"唉 開依個po好似好傻仔 幫我拉得唔得 好驚自爆"},{"pid":"2a2cbb828ebb11730497560b3bd07ab1e0979819","tid":2439842,"uid":136116,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T13:58:46.000Z","msg":"樓主住昇薈+ 有個讀hku 女友 fced"},{"pid":"86373a9451a97fbdc534125f867038a3bb3bdabf","tid":2439842,"uid":306413,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T14:00:23.000Z","msg":"假膠 拉"},{"pid":"e0609091b3e17b43c6b81b35e09641387867768a","tid":2439842,"uid":53798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T14:02:34.000Z","msg":"有錢就得"},{"pid":"17d6ab4cae8da6117cf1bbbdab616baacafa3b51","tid":2439842,"uid":32454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T14:04:13.000Z","msg":"手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{